Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends},
         xfce4-panel (>= 4.16.0)
Description: Full-screen application launcher plugin for XFCE Panel
 A full-screen application launcher plugin for XFCE Panel, similar to
 macOS Launchpad. Features include:
 .
  - Full-screen overlay with semi-transparent background
  - Grid layout showing all installed applications
  - Search functionality to filter applications
  - Smooth hover effects on application icons
  - Hide applications feature
  - Dynamic application detection
  - ESC key to close launcher
